i-MSCP installer/engine hooks
=============================

This directory is intended to store any i-MSCP installer/engine hook files. Hook file present in this directory will be
automatically loaded by i-MSCP at runtime.

An i-MSCP installer/engine hook file is a simple perl script, which defines one or many hook functions registered on the
i-MSCP hooks manager. The naming convention for hooks files is as follow: filename.pl
